## Customization

### Custom Header and Button Text

You can customize the header and button text:

```tsx
<FundCard
  assetSymbol="ETH"
  country="US"
  currency="USD"
  headerText="Purchase Ethereum"
  buttonText="Purchase"
/>
```

<iframe src="https://684b5e62b1ff46bc5bf83966-aijszlfakk.chromatic.com/iframe.html?args=&id=onchainkit-fund-card--with-custom-text&viewMode=story&dark=true&hero=true" width="100%" height="370px" />

