  <Tab value="bash" title="Request (cURL)">
    ```bash lines wrap
    cdpcurl -k /tmp/cdp_api_key.json 'https://api.developer.coinbase.com/onramp/v1/sell/options?country=US&subdivision=NY'
    ```
