  <Tab value="bash" title="Request (cURL)">
    ```bash lines wrap
    cdpcurl -k /tmp/cdp_api_key.json 'https://api.developer.coinbase.com/onramp/v1/sell/user/{partner_user_id}/transactions?page_key={next_page_key}&page_size={page_size}'
    ```
  </Tab>

